<br>
If you don't want to purchase additional gear I'm sure DSL providers sell additional IP's just as cable ones do.  Dynamic is actaully far easier to set up. It's crazy not to purchase the gateway router though since they are simple to set up and pay for themselves within a year.<br>
<br>
The RT311 can be had on Amazon for about $90 and for considerably less on Ebay.  No moving parts, I'd go Ebay.<br>
<br>
